{"tid":1082627,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★飢餓難抵！2賊披雨褸爆竊長沙灣粥店","createTime":"2019-03-29T05:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T05:41:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b73d53ecf4387bd1679d8c3a4b70ce7228662888","tid":1082627,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"長沙灣青山道230號一間粥店發生爆竊案。今日(29日)凌晨3時，大廈保安員巡經後巷，發現粥店鐵門虛掩，懷疑遇竊，於是報警。警方接報到場，聯絡店主返回，發現收銀櫃撬開，經初步點算，失去千多元銀頭。<br />\n<br />\n警員初步調查，相信賊人從後樓梯撬開假天花潛入天井的廚房，再撬毀廚房通往舖面的木門門鎖，進入舖面爆竊，並翻查店舖的「天眼」錄影片段，發現凌晨1時許，2名年約40至50歲，戴Cap帽、口罩及手套男子，披上雨褸潛入店內分頭搜掠，逗留短短不足4分鐘便得手逃去。案件列作爆竊，交深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據職員稱，粥店開業近十年，今次是第一次遇竊，<span style=\"color: red;\">由於店內並無貴重財物，故不明兩名賊人，為何勞師動眾潛入店內犯案</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/bkn-20190329035451111-0329_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fbkn-20190329035451111-0329_00822_001.html&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HejOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=4bdd686e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/bkn-20190329035451111-0329_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"da4cfee5da4a111bdf216a9fe4de28ea46fb1e45","tid":1082627,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"三年零八個月feel"},{"pid":"ab3d501aa62389a4328f56ff501ca38e55501d33","tid":1082627,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329035451111-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190329131622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329035451111-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190329131622&h=f587e23c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a78459d67ba3598488add49da7ad882503e41b0","tid":1082627,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:41:31.00